                        <p><strong>1¬™ Diferen√ßa:</strong></p>
                        <p>27 - (-5) = 32</p>
                        <p>43 - 27 = 16</p>
                        <p>43 - 43 = 0</p>
                        <p>-5 - 43 = -48</p>
                        
                        <p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>2¬™ Diferen√ßa:</strong></p>
